msgid "IDS_DOCK_AMMO_DESCRIPTION_IMPULSELASER"
msgstr "<p>The beams are dual-purpose: they can damage enemies and heal allies.</p><p class=\"p_spacing\"> </p><p>You can cease firing before the laser is completely discharged in order to reduce the recharge time.</p>"

